data.description: No HOA on this beautiful ranch brick house, 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Combo Kitchen and Dining area with tile floor. Convenient access to the garage leading outside both front and backyard. Built-in air cleaner/purifier, HVAC 2017. Huge backyard fully fenced. Enjoy spacious sunroom adjacent to nice patio. House is equipped with Wifi controlled thermostat and garage door. Property may be able to turn into commercial in the future. Close to Greenwood shopping mall, restaurants, and Highway I-65.
